<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 16:09:27 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>哈尼亚之死对哈马斯来说是一个打击，但历史证明总会有替代者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/haniyehs-death-is-a-blow-to-hamas-but-history-proves-theres-always-a-replacement/00000191-089e-dd42-af99-edff95120000</link><description>哈尼亚的遇刺是对哈马斯领导层的威胁，也是对伊朗和真主党的挑衅。尽管如此，这并不是一场“组织地震”，哈马斯政治局的其他几名成员可以轻松取代他</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 14:56:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/haniyehs-death-is-a-blow-to-hamas-but-history-proves-theres-always-a-replacement/00000191-089e-dd42-af99-edff95120000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的暗杀政策只会让哈马斯、真主党和伊朗更加坚定</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/israels-assassination-policy-only-makes-hamas-hezbollah-and-iran-more-determined/00000191-08b7-d3e8-adbd-b8f7eced0000</link><description>伊斯梅尔·哈尼亚和福阿德·舒克在德黑兰和贝鲁特的暗杀事件展示了以色列的能力，但定点清除的学说本身已成为目的，而不是实现实际战略目标的一种方式</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 14:03:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/israels-assassination-policy-only-makes-hamas-hezbollah-and-iran-more-determined/00000191-08b7-d3e8-adbd-b8f7eced0000</guid></item><item><title>别跟我谈论战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/dont-talk-to-me-about-the-war/00000191-08fe-d61c-a5bb-fefeeb780000</link><description>以色列市场和消费者似乎没有意识到以色列在本周发生两起暗杀事件后面临的风险。否认主义一直是加沙战争的主题</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 13:46:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/dont-talk-to-me-about-the-war/00000191-08fe-d61c-a5bb-fefeeb780000</guid></item><item><title>哈尼亚在伊朗首都被杀后，电视节目“德黑兰”的以色列明星分享了含糊其辞的信息</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/israeli-star-of-tv-show-tehran-shares-coy-message-after-haniyeh-killed-in-iran/00000191-08cb-dd56-a9f5-69cbaf2b0000</link><description>出生于耶路撒冷的女演员尼夫·苏丹 (Niv Sultan) 在 Apple TV 间谍惊悚片中饰演摩萨德特工，她在社交媒体帖子中对着镜头眨眼，巧妙地暗示她的角色参与其中。以色列尚未确认对哈尼亚遇刺事件负责</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 13:29:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/israeli-star-of-tv-show-tehran-shares-coy-message-after-haniyeh-killed-in-iran/00000191-08cb-dd56-a9f5-69cbaf2b0000</guid></item><item><title>“为什么现在杀他”：以色列人质家庭担心哈尼亚被杀对停火协议的影响</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/haniyehs-killing-raises-concern-among-hostages-families-over-impact-to-cease-fire-deal/00000191-0735-dd56-a9f5-6f77efef0000</link><description>“为什么现在既然已经达成协议，他们却选择杀了他？”一名人质的亲戚问道。虽然哈尼亚之死的影响很难预测，但它可能会软化以色列现在已经取得“胜利形象”的立场</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 12:33:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/haniyehs-killing-raises-concern-among-hostages-families-over-impact-to-cease-fire-deal/00000191-0735-dd56-a9f5-6f77efef0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡办公室拒绝透露参加锡安之翼飞往美国航班的乘客名单</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-office-refuses-to-disclose-list-of-passengers-on-wing-of-zion-flight-to-u-s/00000191-0863-d3e8-adbd-b8f756f80000</link><description>据报道，总理的儿子亚伊尔·内塔尼亚胡本周返回以色列，该办公室还拒绝回答他是否登上了从华盛顿返回的航班。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 12:10:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-office-refuses-to-disclose-list-of-passengers-on-wing-of-zion-flight-to-u-s/00000191-0863-d3e8-adbd-b8f756f80000</guid></item><item><title>以色列和真主党之间的“反应方程”已达到极限，但尚未被撕裂</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/the-response-equation-between-israel-and-hezbollah-is-stretched-to-its-limits/00000191-0859-dc27-abdb-fe79d0bb0000</link><description>迈季代勒沙姆斯的致命袭击并不是全面战争合理性的转折点，但它迫使双方做出回应，即使没有战略利益。真主党的反应还取决于黎巴嫩的内部事态发展，黎巴嫩自身的利益和伊朗的利益都在黎巴嫩</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 11:15:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/the-response-equation-between-israel-and-hezbollah-is-stretched-to-its-limits/00000191-0859-dc27-abdb-fe79d0bb0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯称政治领袖伊斯梅尔·哈尼亚在德黑兰被杀，情况尚不清楚</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/hamas-says-political-leader-ismail-haniyeh-killed-in-tehran-circumstances-unclear/00000191-0829-d117-abd9-8d6f43c50000</link><description>这位长期担任政治局领导人、前巴勒斯坦总理于周三凌晨 2 点左右在伊朗首都被暗杀。中东新闻网站称他被从伊朗境外发射的精确制导导弹杀死</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 10:39:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/hamas-says-political-leader-ismail-haniyeh-killed-in-tehran-circumstances-unclear/00000191-0829-d117-abd9-8d6f43c50000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗和黎巴嫩的暗杀事件将中东推向地区战争的边缘</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/assassinations-in-iran-and-lebanon-pushed-mideast-to-the-edge-of-a-regional-war/00000191-07e5-dd56-a9f5-6fe743d30000</link><description>以色列尚未对伊斯梅尔·哈尼亚在德黑兰遇刺事件承担正式责任，但伊朗不太可能对发生在自己领土上的袭击置之不理。哈尼亚被杀也减少了人质交易谈判取得突破的机会</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 09:57:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/assassinations-in-iran-and-lebanon-pushed-mideast-to-the-edge-of-a-regional-war/00000191-07e5-dd56-a9f5-6fe743d30000</guid></item><item><title>军事法庭延长对八名涉嫌性虐待加沙被拘留者的士兵的逮捕期限</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/military-court-extends-arrest-of-8-soldiers-suspected-of-sexually-abusing-gazan-detainee/00000191-07c2-d3e8-adbd-bfd69e370000</link><description>八名士兵的拘留已延长至周日。据称，他们属于 Sde Teiman 的“核心圈子”，对虐待事件知情，但对于巴勒斯坦被拘留者在他们看守期间如何受伤给出了相互矛盾的解释</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 08:22:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/military-court-extends-arrest-of-8-soldiers-suspected-of-sexually-abusing-gazan-detainee/00000191-07c2-d3e8-adbd-bfd69e370000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗称哈尼亚暗杀“懦弱”，世界对他的死感到震惊</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/iran-says-haniyeh-assassination-cowardly-as-world-reacts-with-shock-to-his-death/00000191-0795-d3e8-adbd-bfd7d05b0000</link><description>哈马斯政治领导人伊斯梅尔·哈尼亚在伊朗中部被杀后，外交部和政府发言人迅速发出谴责，称这是“危险的升级”。尽管美国没有谴责或庆祝，但他们发誓要保护以色列免受袭击</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 07:59:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/iran-says-haniyeh-assassination-cowardly-as-world-reacts-with-shock-to-his-death/00000191-0795-d3e8-adbd-bfd7d05b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队任命备受争议的巴拉克·希拉姆将军为加沙师指挥官</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/idf-appoints-controversial-general-barak-hiram-to-commander-of-gaza-division/00000191-07ae-dd56-a9f5-6fefb7420000</link><description>10 月 7 日，希勒姆指挥的部队向贝埃里基布兹的一处民宅发射了坦克炮弹，里面有人质。尽管一些贝埃里家族对这一决定存在分歧，但海勒姆相信他最适合担任这一职务</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 07:51:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/idf-appoints-controversial-general-barak-hiram-to-commander-of-gaza-division/00000191-07ae-dd56-a9f5-6fefb7420000</guid></item><item><title>在德黑兰被暗杀的哈马斯政治领导人伊斯梅尔·哈尼亚是谁？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/hamas-confirms-its-political-leader-ismail-haniyeh-killed-in-tehran/00000191-06d9-d117-abd9-8ffff56e0000</link><description>该恐怖组织表示，哈尼亚在参加伊朗新总统的宣誓就职仪式后，在“犹太复国主义分子对他在德黑兰的住所进行的一次危险的袭击”中被杀。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 03:39:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/hamas-confirms-its-political-leader-ismail-haniyeh-killed-in-tehran/00000191-06d9-d117-abd9-8ffff56e0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡只能从袭击以色列国防军两个基地的混乱分子中获益</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-only-stands-to-gain-from-the-agents-of-chaos-who-stormed-two-idf-bases/00000191-0531-df85-a399-ed37094d0000</link><description>将两个军事基地的暴力袭击与特拉维夫的民主示威活动（以色列总理似乎所做的那样）进行比较，引起了我们自 10 月 7 日以来从未经历过的担忧</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 03:01:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-only-stands-to-gain-from-the-agents-of-chaos-who-stormed-two-idf-bases/00000191-0531-df85-a399-ed37094d0000</guid></item><item><title>Gallant：以色列不希望局势升级，继续努力解决人质问题</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article-live/idf-hezbollah-fired-20-rockets-at-northern-israel-sparking-widespread-fire/00000191-069d-dc27-abdb-f6fd48370000</link><description>半岛电视台称，其两名记者在以色列对加沙的袭击中丧生 ■ 以色列因安全局势关闭北部领空 ■ 英国外交大臣和国防部长在卡塔尔推动结束加沙冲突的努力 ■ 伊朗的联合国使命：回应哈尼亚遇刺将令人遗憾 ■ 以色列人在约旦河西岸刺伤袭击后伤势严重 ■ “卑鄙行为”：巴勒斯坦总统阿巴斯谴责在德黑兰杀害哈马斯领导人汉尼耶 ■ 以色列关闭哈德拉以北领空</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 02:46:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article-live/idf-hezbollah-fired-20-rockets-at-northern-israel-sparking-widespread-fire/00000191-069d-dc27-abdb-f6fd48370000</guid></item><item><title>国土报卡通</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/00000191-054c-d130-a5bf-b5ce54e30000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 20:21:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/00000191-054c-d130-a5bf-b5ce54e30000</guid></item><item><title>死者家属会见以色列国防军指挥官，指挥官下令用坦克向贝埃里基布兹的家开火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/families-of-killed-hostages-meet-with-idf-officer-who-ordered-tank-fire-on-kibbutz-home/00000191-045b-d117-abd9-8d7f73700000</link><description>基布兹的一份声明称，大多数受害者家属在结束对话时都感到和解，并对哈马斯袭击事件有了更好的了解。会议几小时后，以色列国防军宣布任命他为加沙师指挥官</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 19:46:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/families-of-killed-hostages-meet-with-idf-officer-who-ordered-tank-fire-on-kibbutz-home/00000191-045b-d117-abd9-8d7f73700000</guid></item><item><title>“他们向我吐口水，称我为荡妇”：记者在以色列国防军基地遭到极右暴徒袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/they-spit-on-me-called-me-a-slut-journalists-attacked-by-far-right-mob-at-idf-base/00000191-0461-dc27-abdb-f6714c350000</link><description>周一，右翼抗议者对前来报道斯德·泰曼拘留中心袭击事件的多名以色列记者进行辱骂、吐口水和人身攻击。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 18:41:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/they-spit-on-me-called-me-a-slut-journalists-attacked-by-far-right-mob-at-idf-base/00000191-0461-dc27-abdb-f6714c350000</guid></item><item><title>要成为一个文明国家，以色列必须承认自己的野蛮行为</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/to-be-a-civilized-nation-israel-must-acknowledge-its-own-barbarism/00000191-04b6-df85-a399-edb6e2860000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡不能两全其美。他不能试图将以色列描绘成一个开明的民主国家，保卫自己（和西方世界）免受残酷怪物的侵害，同时也容忍那些不认为针对可能的恐怖分子的野蛮行为的指控应该受到调查的部长们</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 18:01:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/to-be-a-civilized-nation-israel-must-acknowledge-its-own-barbarism/00000191-04b6-df85-a399-edb6e2860000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 298 天：以色列国防军称其目标是真主党二号人物</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-298-idf-says-it-targeted-hezbollahs-second-in-command/00000191-04a7-dc27-abdb-f6f7ca3b0000</link><description>以色列平民被黎巴嫩火箭弹弹片炸死 ■ 以色列国防军消息人士称，被扣押在加沙的一些人质尸体将永远找不到袭击以色列国防军基地的右翼暴徒 ■ 据报道，英国已决定推迟停止向以色列出口武器的决定 ■ 战争进入 298 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 17:29:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-298-idf-says-it-targeted-hezbollahs-second-in-command/00000191-04a7-dc27-abdb-f6f7ca3b0000</guid></item></channel></rss>